You need a high quality product to compete successfully in the
market. To improve your products' quality, you have to invest in
R&D to find new ways to produce better products.

In this tutorial, the following hot keys are available:

[Esc]              - Quit the tutorial.
[Back Space] - Go back one tutorial step.

In this lesson, you will learn how to set up an R&D center, start
R&D projects, and apply the research results to your business.

