Now click the "Layout" button to see the layout plan for your
R&D center.

You can set up a maximum of nine R&D units in an R&D center. They
can work independently as nine separate teams or be linked
into a large team for increased performance.

An R&D team with three or four units is reasonable if you are not
too aggressive or too conservative towards R&D.

